summary: Modify skeleton, you can use high heels.
descriptionHtml:
==================
  Rhaos HighHeel 
==================

First, im sorry my bad english.

This Mod gives you a new skeleton_female.nif for a highheel

and an example(and simple) high heel mesh as a replacement of an ebony boots.

The new skel_female.nif is a modification of original skyrim skeleton_female.nif.

My images show you what is modified

There are 2 version, one is for original skyrim, other is for cbbe body.

This Mod doesnt include body mesh ,including only skeleton files for female characters.


If you make a high heel mesh with this mod, you should use a skeleton file of this mod, not an original skeleton.
author: Rhaos
